FuncDef: This command specifies an IPv4 route (prefix/length) per subscriber-interface to be exported (announced) to indicate liveness of the subscriber-interface on the WLAN-GW. This route is the one that is monitored in routing by the peer WLAN-GW to decide its state with respect.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the IP prefix and length. Values-ip-prefix:a.b.c.d.
